{
  "key": 18323,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnAreYouCatchingPokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "Dawn: Hi, {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}!\n",
        "Hope your battles went well!\r",
        "Let me show you the Pokemon\n",
        "School of Jubilife City!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnWowYouveAlreadyGotNumPokemonWithYou",
      "en_US": [
        "Wow! You’ve already got {STRVAR_1 50, 0, 0} Pokémon\n",
        "with you!\r",
        "At that pace, your Pokédex should\n",
        "be full in no time at all!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnIThinkYoudFeelALotSaferIfYouWereToCatchSomeMore",
      "en_US": [
        "...Um...\r",
        "I think you’d feel a lot safer if you\n",
        "were to catch some more.\r",
        "You know, like when you need to travel\n",
        "to faraway places.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnFollowMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh, I know! Don’t you think it’s\n",
        "better to know more about Pokémon?\r",
        "Sure it is!\n",
        "I know just the place.\r",
        "Come on!\n",
        "Don’t be shy. Follow me!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasHowManyPokemonhaveYouCaught",
      "en_US": [
        "Lucas: Hey, {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}!\n",
        "Hope your battles went well!\r",
        "Let me show you the Pokemon\n",
        "School of Jubilife City!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasWhoaYouAlreadyHaveNumPokemonWithYou",
      "en_US": [
        "Whoa! You already have {STRVAR_1 50, 0, 0} Pokémon\n",
        "with you!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasIThinkYouShouldCatchSomeMore",
      "en_US": [
        "Huh?\n",
        "I think you should catch some more.\r",
        "It might be more of a challenge\n",
        "raising a lot of Pokémon...\r",
        "But it’s worth it. The more Pokémon\n",
        "you have, the happier you’ll be.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasFollowMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Hey, that’s right! Don’t you think it’s\n",
        "better to know more about Pokémon?\r",
        "Sure it is!\n",
        "There’s this great place for that.\r",
        "Come on! It’s all right.\n",
        "Follow me.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnThatManWhatIsHeDoing",
      "en_US": [
        "Dawn: That man...\n",
        "What is he doing?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnUm",
      "en_US": "Dawn: Um..."
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasThatGuyWhatsHeDoing",
      "en_US": [
        "Lucas: That guy...\n",
        "What’s he doing?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasUhExcuse",
      "en_US": "Lucas: Uh, excuse..."
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_WHAAAT",
      "en_US": "WHAAAT?!\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_HowDidYouUnmaskMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Mysterious man: ...How did you know\n",
        "I’m an undercover investiagtor?!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnIWasJustMakingConversation",
      "en_US": [
        "Dawn: Huh? What? I beg your pardon?\n",
        "I was just making conversation...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasIWasJustMakingSmallTalk",
      "en_US": [
        "Lucas: Huh? What? Are you kidding?\n",
        "I was just making small talk...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_IKnowBetterNotToBelieveThat",
      "en_US": [
        "Shady man: ...Heh. You claim you were\n",
        "only making conversation, do you?\r",
        "But, I know better not to believe that.\n",
        "No, no, no.\r",
        "You recognized right away that I was\n",
        "someone extraordinary.\r",
        "That is why you spoke to me, is it not?\n",
        "Your power of observation is fearsome!\r",
        "Quite admirable, you are!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_IsTheSayingDontBeAThiefFamiliarToYou",
      "en_US": [
        "Shady man: My code name, it is Looker.\n",
        "It is what they all call me.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_TakingWhatBelongsToOthersIsWrong",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: Yes, that is correct.\n",
        "Taking what belongs to others is wrong.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_YouClaimToNotKnowIt",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: No? You claim to not know it?\n",
        "How could that be?\r",
        "Perhaps your mama has said it, but you\n",
        "have forgotten it, like usual?\r",
        "Now listen, my friends. It is wrong to\n",
        "take what belongs to others.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_PerhapsYouCanMakeUseOfThis",
      "en_US": [
        "Incidentally, you are Trainers, yes?\n",
        "Perhaps you can make use of these?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_ThatVsRecorderItIsANiftyDeviceForRecordingAMatch",
      "en_US": [
        "I got these as a gift, but have no\n",
        "use for them.\r",
        "Myself, I do not do Pokémon\n",
        "battling very often.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_YouMustInformMeOfAnyHappenings",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: Also, I have a request.\r",
        "If you were to see me again, I ask that\n",
        "you not talk to me, for I am on duty.\r",
        "...Actually, yes, yes, you may speak to\n",
        "me. You must.\r",
        "Not because I am lonely, no, no!\n",
        "You must inform me of any happenings!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnWorkingForTheInternationPoliceMustBeHard",
      "en_US": [
        "Dawn: Anyway...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnHereItIsItsTheTrainersSchool",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}, here it is.\n",
        "It’s the Trainers’ School.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnISawYourFriendRivalGoInEarlier",
      "en_US": [
        "I saw your friend {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0} go in\n",
        "earlier.\r",
        "He could still be in there studying.\n",
        "OK, bye now!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasWorkingForTheInternationPoliceSoundsHard",
      "en_US": [
        "Lucas: ...Working for the International\n",
        "Police sounds hard.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasHereWeAreThisIsTheTrainersSchool",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}, here we are.\n",
        "This is the Trainers’ School.\f",
        "The name says it all!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasYourPalRivalWentInEarier",
      "en_US": [
        "Your pal {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0} went in earlier.\n",
        "He might still be studying in there.\r",
        "OK, see you around!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_JubilifeCitysBuiltOnLandTheyCarvedOutOfAMountain",
      "en_US": [
        "Jubilife City’s built on land they\n",
        "carved out of a mountain.\r",
        "The people and Pokémon of Oreburgh\n",
        "City helped out with that undertaking."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_HaveYouPaidAVisitToTheTVStation",
      "en_US": [
        "Hello! Let me ask you, have you paid\n",
        "a visit to the TV station?\r",
        "If you’ve never been, you owe it to\n",
        "yourself to make the trip.\r",
        "And, if you’ve been there before,\n",
        "it never hurts to visit again.\r",
        "After all, you can be a star!\n",
        "Or at least dream of being one!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_ItIsYouHaveYouVisitedTheTrainersSchool",
      "en_US": [
        "Ah, it is you! Have no fear.\n",
        "There are no shady characters about.\r",
        "Incidentally, have you visited the\n",
        "Trainers’ School?\r",
        "Did your friend not guide you there\n",
        "earlier?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_HelloMyFriendHaveYouVisitedTheTrainersSchool",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: Hello, my friend.\n",
        "Have you visited the Trainers’ School?\r",
        "Did your friend not guide you there\n",
        "earlier?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_ItIsYouHaveYouNotObtainedAPoketch",
      "en_US": [
        "Ah, it is you! Have no fear.\n",
        "There are no shady characters about.\r",
        "Incidentally, have you not obtained\n",
        "a Pokétch?\r",
        "I believe a Pokétch is now free in\n",
        "exchange for some Coupons?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_TellMeHaveYouNotObtainedAPoketch",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: Tell me, have you not obtained\n",
        "a Pokétch?\r",
        "I believe a Pokétch is now free in\n",
        "exchange for some Coupons?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_ItIsYouHaveYouNotObtainedAGymBadge",
      "en_US": [
        "Ah, it is you! Have no fear.\n",
        "There are no shady characters about.\r",
        "Incidentally, have you not obtained\n",
        "a Gym Badge?\r",
        "I believe you receive one for defeating\n",
        "the Gym Leader at a Pokémon Gym?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_TellMeHaveYouNotObtainedAPalPad",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: Tell me, have you not obtained\n",
        "a Pal Pad?\r",
        "Is not a Pal Pad free to anyone visiting\n",
        "the Pokémon Center’s basement?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_ISeeThatYouHaveObtainedItAPalPadForYourself",
      "en_US": [
        "Ah, yes. I see that you have obtained\n",
        "it, a Pal Pad for yourself.\r",
        "I myself, a member of the International\n",
        "Police, the fighters of crime around the\f",
        "world, have one also.\r",
        "For it is what one must have to trade\n",
        "Pokémon with Trainers around the world.\r",
        "Take that Pal Pad to the Global Terminal\n",
        "for trading on an international level!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_IShallTakeMyInvestigationElsewhere",
      "en_US": [
        "Anyway, there appears to be no one\n",
        "shady in this Jubilife City.\r",
        "I shall therefore take my investigation\n",
        "elsewhere.\r",
        "But, my friend, I suggest you remain\n",
        "vigilant for shady grown-ups!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_YouCallYourselfAPokemonTrainerAndYetYouHaveNoPoketch",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh, oh, oh?\r",
        "You call yourself a Pokémon Trainer?\n",
        "And yet you have no Pokétch?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_AllYouHaveToDoIsFindThreeClownsInJubilifeCity",
      "en_US": [
        "You see, I invented Pokétches and\n",
        "want you to have one too!\r",
        "All you have to do is find three\n",
        "clowns in Jubilife City.\r",
        "If you can find them...\n",
        "I will gift you with a Pokétch!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_CollectACouponFromEachClownThenComeSeeMeOK",
      "en_US": [
        "The three clowns will each ask you\n",
        "a skill-testing question.\r",
        "Collect a Coupon from each clown,\n",
        "then come see me, OK?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_InReturnForTheseCouponsIPresentYouThisPokemonWatch",
      "en_US": [
        "OK, let me count your Coupons!\n",
        "One, two, three!\r",
        "Bravo! I say, bravo!\r",
        "In return for these Coupons,\n",
        "I present you this Pokétch!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_PlayerReceivedAPoketch",
      "en_US": "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} received a {COLOR 1}Pokétch{COLOR 0}!{YESNO 1}"
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_YouCanAddAppsToYourPoketch",
      "en_US": [
        "You can add apps to your Pokétch\n",
        "to make it even more versatile!\r",
        "Touch the Pokétch screen and find the\n",
        "apps that are right for you!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DoesAPokemonGrowByDefeatingOthersAndGainingExpPoints",
      "en_US": [
        "Hi! I’m a Pokétch campaign clown!\n",
        "Let’s roll out my question!\r",
        "Does a Pokémon grow by defeating\n",
        "others and gaining Exp. Points?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DingDingYoureAbsolutelyCorrect1",
      "en_US": [
        "Ding-ding!\n",
        "You’re absolutely correct!\r",
        "But did you really understand?\n",
        "Show me!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_BzzzztThatsTheWrongAnswer1",
      "en_US": [
        "Bzzzzt!\n",
        "That’s the wrong answer..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_PokemonGrowStrongerByDefeatingOtherPokemonInBattle",
      "en_US": [
        "Pokémon grow stronger by defeating\n",
        "other Pokémon in battle.\r",
        "Some Pokémon even grow into an\n",
        "entirely different form in a process\f",
        "known as evolution.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_HereYouGoYourPoketchCoupon1",
      "en_US": [
        "Seems like you got it!\n",
        "Your Pokétch Coupon!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_PokemonGrowStrongerThroughBattling",
      "en_US": [
        "Pokémon grow stronger through\n",
        "battling.\r",
        "Some Pokémon even grow into an\n",
        "entirely different form in a process\f",
        "known as evolution."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_AskJustLikePokemonTypesTheMovesOfPokemonAlsoHaveTypes",
      "en_US": [
        "Hi! I’m a Pokétch campaign clown!\n",
        "Let’s roll out my question!\r",
        "Just like Pokémon types, the moves\n",
        "of Pokémon also have types?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DingDingYoureAbsolutelyCorrect2",
      "en_US": [
        "Ding-ding!\n",
        "You’re absolutely correct!\r",
        "But did you really understand?\n",
        "Show me!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_BzzzztThatsTheWrongAnswer2",
      "en_US": [
        "Bzzzzt!\n",
        "That’s the wrong answer..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_IfThePokemonsTypeMatchesItsMovesTypeThatMoveIsMadeMuchMorePowerful",
      "en_US": [
        "If the Pokémon’s type matches its\n",
        "move’s type, that move is made much\f",
        "more powerful!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_HereYouGoYourPoketchCoupon2",
      "en_US": [
        "Seems like you got it!\n",
        "Your Pokétch Coupon!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_IfThePokemonsTypeMatchesItsMovesTypeThatMoveIsMadeMuchMorePowerful2",
      "en_US": [
        "If the Pokémon’s type matches its\n",
        "move’s type, that move is made much\f",
        "more powerful!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_CanAPokemonHoldAnItem",
      "en_US": [
        "Hi! I’m a Pokétch campaign clown!\n",
        "Let’s roll out my question!\r",
        "Can a Pokémon hold an item?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DingDingYoureAbsolutelyCorrect3",
      "en_US": [
        "Ding-ding!\n",
        "You’re absolutely correct!\r",
        "But did you really understand?\n",
        "Show me!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_BzzzztThatsTheWrongAnswer3",
      "en_US": [
        "Bzzzzt!\n",
        "That’s the wrong answer..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_APokemonMayHoldASingleItem",
      "en_US": [
        "A Pokémon may hold a single item.\r",
        "Some items become effective as soon\n",
        "as they are held by a Pokémon.\r",
        "Berries are eaten by Pokémon as\n",
        "necessary during battle.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_HereYouGoYourPoketchCoupon3",
      "en_US": [
        "Seems like you got it!\n",
        "Your Pokétch Coupon!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_YouShouldStickAround",
      "en_US": [
        "Hi, there. You should stick around.\n",
        "We’re doing a Pokétch campaign soon.\r",
        "Before it starts, I think you should\n",
        "brush up at the Trainers’ School."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_APokemonMayHoldASingleItem2",
      "en_US": [
        "A Pokémon may hold a single item.\r",
        "Some items become effective as soon\n",
        "as they are held by Pokémon.\r",
        "Berries are eaten by Pokémon as\n",
        "necessary during battle."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_HandOverAllYourResearchFindings",
      "en_US": [
        "Mystery man: Professor, you must comply!\n",
        "Hand over all your research findings.\r",
        "Failure to comply will result in a painful\n",
        "time for your assistant.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_ThatsOreburghsGymBadgeISee",
      "en_US": [
        "Rowan: Ah, {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}.\n",
        "Well? How is the Pokédex progressing?\r",
        "That’s Oreburgh’s Gym Badge, I see.\n",
        "Very impressive! You’re a natural!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_OhProfessorOfRowanMustYouBeSoDifficult",
      "en_US": [
        "Mystery man: Must you be so difficult?\n",
        "This is work for us.\r",
        "What we’re saying is--we demand\n",
        "you comply with our demands.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_WhyMustYouBeSuchANuisance",
      "en_US": [
        "Rowan: Quiet, you lot!\n",
        "Why must you be such a nuisance?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_MyGoodnessYouCallYourselvesAdults",
      "en_US": [
        "My goodness...\n",
        "You call yourselves adults?\r",
        "You kids, don’t grow up to be like these\n",
        "sorry specimens.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_WeWillMakeYouRegretInsultingTeamGalactic",
      "en_US": [
        "Mystery man: Eeeeeh!\n",
        "You had to make this personal!\r",
        "We will make you regret insulting\n",
        "Team Galactic!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_YouKidsGiveTheseThugsALessonInCivilityPlease",
      "en_US": [
        "Rowan: You kids, give these thugs a\n",
        "lesson in civility, please.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnPlayerLetsBattleTogether",
      "en_US": [
        "Dawn: {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}!\n",
        "Let’s battle together!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasPlayerJoinMeAndBattleTheseGuys",
      "en_US": [
        "Lucas: {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}!\n",
        "Join me and battle these guys!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_WeWillRetreatForNow",
      "en_US": [
        "Grunt 1: You leave us no option.\n",
        "We will retreat for now.\r",
        "We shall do so because Team Galactic\n",
        "is benevolent to all.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_ThatLotTheyCalledThemselvesTeamGalactic",
      "en_US": [
        "Rowan: That lot...\n",
        "They called themselves Team Galactic.\r",
        "When Pokémon evolve, they seem to\n",
        "release some type of energy...\r",
        "However, I believe that it’s a mystic\n",
        "power far beyond our control.\r",
        "But Team Galactic seems to be studying\n",
        "that power’s potential.\r",
        "They want to know if it can be used as\n",
        "energy for something...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_DawnTheProfessorStudiesTheEvolutionOfPokemonToo",
      "en_US": [
        "Dawn: {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}, did you know?\r",
        "The professor studies the evolution\n",
        "of Pokémon, too.\r",
        "According to his research, 90% of all\n",
        "Pokémon are somehow tied to evolution!\r",
        "Well, maybe that’s the reason those\n",
        "people tried to take the professor’s\f",
        "research data by force.\r",
        "That’s really unforgivable!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_LucasTheProfessorStudiesTheEvolutionOfPokemonToo",
      "en_US": [
        "Lucas: {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}, did you know\n",
        "about this?\r",
        "The professor studies the\n",
        "evolution of Pokémon, too.\r",
        "According to his research, 90% of all\n",
        "Pokémon are somehow tied to evolution!\r",
        "Maybe that’s the reason those goons\n",
        "tried to take the professor’s\f",
        "research data.\f",
        "They’re not allowed to do that!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_WhyDontYouCollectAllTheGymBadgesOfSinnoh",
      "en_US": [
        "Rowan: Thanks to you two, nothing came\n",
        "of that situation. I appreciate that.\r",
        "Incidentally, {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}.\n",
        "Kudos to you for your battling skill.\r",
        "It got me thinking. Why don’t you\n",
        "collect all the Gym Badges of Sinnoh?\r",
        "Either way, I wish you the best of luck\n",
        "on your journey. Take care now.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "JubilifeCity_Text_OhThatWasVeryGood",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh, that was very good!\n",
        "Nicely done! Truly excellent!\r",
